text: Ana María Rendón Martínez is an archer from Colombia. She was born on 10 March 1986. Rendón competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics, 2012 Summer Olympics, and 2016 Summer Olympics.Ana María RendónAna Maria RENDON == References == Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Colombian archers Category:Olympians for Colombia
